Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:41.05,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}As illusions start to gain colour and shapes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:44.97,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}While they slowly start to become real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:47.18,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}I will give them form
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:49.81,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}And grant their wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:53.06,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}As the gently blowing wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:57.19,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}Stirs the pages of an aged book
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.44,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}I may turn back now and then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.53,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}But rest assured, it will be all right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:05.32,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}Tales of meeting and parting once more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:09.41,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}All so full of new, yet-unexplored things
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:16.50,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}I gently brushed the words set down in blurry ink
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:19.54,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}Where are you going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:22.21,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}Somewhere just a little far away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:25.88,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}Let the things I left behind turn into dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:30.35,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}Choosing what I like best, and in the process
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:34.10,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}Slowly growing into myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.90,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}"Oh, do let us meet again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:38.90,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}"And make it a promise, too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:42.15,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}You said to me, grinning from ear to ear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:45.07,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}"Yes, let us meet again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.20,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}Linking fingers, we sealed our vow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:49.57,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}And as I heard a voice calling to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:51.49,EP1_OP,eng,0,0,0,,{\1a&HC8&\blur4\fad(200,200)}I opened my eyes
